text: Asmelash Geyesus (born 22 March 1968) is an Ethiopian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Ethiopian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Ethiopia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
